# CSS Stylesheets

### Projected Time


### Motivation
I want to create advanced stylesheets.

### Objective
**Students will be able to** do something that we'll list here:
- create an external CSS stylesheet
- link the stylesheet from their page header


### Specific Things To Teach
- how to create a new file
- where to save the file
- how to make a comment in CSS
- nested CSS selectors (`div.green-zone p`)

